The paper discusses tag systems, which are a type of formal language and automata theory. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.FL (Formal Languages and Automata Theory). The paper also discusses the solvability and unsolvability of tag systems, which relates to computational complexity and decision problems. This suggests that the paper could also belong to cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics) and cs.CC (Computational Complexity). The paper also mentions computer experiments, which suggests that it could belong to cs.IT (Information Theory) or cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science).
